previous.excerpt:
Learn more about Steam Deck and reserve yours at at http://steamdeck.com

One of the most frequently asked questions we've received about Steam Deck is about the components inside it, and whether they're replaceable or upgradable. The answer is a bit more complicated than just a yes or no, so we've made a video to explain all the details. Spoiler alert: we DON'T recommend replacing parts yourself, but we still want you to have all of the relevant information about Steam Deck's components. 

Anyway, this is the first public look at what's inside the device, so we hope you enjoy it. 

See this update on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/news/app/1675180/view/3011210954776539264

--
Li-ion battery video seen at 0:45 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=24fYrV2vCPk

next.excerpt:
LAKERS at SUNS | NBA PRESEASON FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 6, 2021

The Phoenix Suns defeated the Los Angeles Lakers, 117-105. Deandre Ayton recorded 14 PTS and 11 REB for the Suns, while Chris Paul added 8 PTS and 11 AST in the victory. Anthony Davis tallied 14 PTS, 8 REB and 2 BLK for the Lakers, while Carmelo Anthony added 8 PTS in the losing effort.

The Suns improve to 1-1 in the preseason, while the Lakers fall to 0-2.

Next Games:
Los Angeles Lakers vs. Golden State Warriors - October 8 at 10pm/et on NBA TV
Phoenix Suns vs. Los Angeles Lakers - October 10 at 10pm/et on ESPN
